title: Good quality; Packages arrive
text:
I love SHEIN :D! The quality of my clothes have been consistently good. They’re not the most comfortable items I own, but they’re surprisingly well-made, considering the price.

If you’re skeptical about items not arriving or them stealing your information, I can assure you it’s never happened to me.

I use pre-paid VISA debit cards to purchase SHEIN e-gift cards just in case. The e-gift cards have exact same amount you buy them for— buy a $50 card for $50, etc. No fees.

All of my items have arrived on time, if not EARLIER than what was expected. Shipping is usually $3.99 but you can use coupons and SHEIN points, which earns you up to 50% off.

I highly suggest buying off of SHEIN<3
